LENGTH TARGETS:

**EARNINGS TRANSCRIPTS:** 3,000-4,500 words
- Q&A Highlights should be 30-40% of total (1,000-1,500 words)
- Bottom Line: 100-150 words
- Other sections: Scale to content richness

**PRESS RELEASES:** 800-1,500 words (scale to announcement substance)
- Major M&A/earnings: 1,200-1,800 words
- Product launch/partnership: 800-1,200 words
- Routine update: 500-800 words

COMPREHENSIVE > BREVITY. Include ALL material facts with quantification.